          <li>Authenticated original judgment or award with court certification or apostille</li>
          <li>MOJ-certified Arabic translation of judgment and supporting documents</li>
          <li>Proof of proper service on defendant in the original proceedings</li>
          <li>Evidence that judgment is final and enforceable in the issuing jurisdiction</li>
          <li>For arbitration awards: the arbitration agreement and evidence of proper procedure</li>
